net.fathomsoft.nova.tree

Class LoopInitialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.Node
      • net.fathomsoft.nova.tree.LoopInitialization

  • public class LoopInitialization
extends Node
    Node extension that represents the initialization section of the for loop. For instance: "for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++)" the first section containing "int i = 0" is the initialization section.
